{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781755557592,"sessionID":"ses_12718501effeJJTfPZxos2yLxP","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_qf93NUJhY2GiFqwN81MmtTKT","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/021-cooperative-heavy-phases\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review/lineages/gpt55-p021b-1\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55-p021b-1-1781755522521-77gcjs\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review/lineages/gpt55-p021b-1 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review/lineages/gpt55-p021b-1. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review/lineages/gpt55-p021b-1.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-p021b-1","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/021-cooperative-heavy-phases","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55-p021b-1-1781755522521-77gcjs","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55-p021b-1-1781755522521-77gcjs\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55-p021b-1-1781755522521-77gcjs\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55-p021b-1-1781755522521-77gcjs\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 229,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781755551790,"end":1781755557590}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_02e2e2b8b41bc887016a336e94d1b48191bccc6cc95b0acccc"}},"id":"prt_ed8e7f557001V2IFGMEfpDhSRI","sessionID":"ses_12718501effeJJTfPZxos2yLxP","messageID":"msg_ed8e7b68a001pfHNA6dXs2Fh6S"}}
